title: Freestyle Thursday:   Travel Memories and Tears
description: With no plans at all for what we were going to talk about, we ended up discussing Europe travel memories, Megxit, and quarantine feelings. There was some audio problems. And some tears. But we prevailed because that's what homemakers do.
